00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:41,510
Do you know how the five regions became the current five regions?

23
00:01:41,510 --> 00:01:45,000
The current Megrez Empire was appointed by Holy Land Firmament

24
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:49,050
to overlord three nations, which are Deep Water, Plough, and Heaven Fiend.

25
00:01:49,050 --> 00:01:51,680
The nation prospers, and the people are at peace.

26
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:55,850
However, a hundred thousand years ago, Di Feitian massacred the five regions.

27
00:01:55,850 --> 00:01:58,160
People were in great misery and suffering.

28
00:01:58,160 --> 00:02:00,960
The elder of Firmament, Chang Qingzi,

29
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:05,420
used Mystic Spirit Leaf to turn around the war situation.

30
00:02:09,220 --> 00:02:13,130
However, Di Feitian didn't just disappear just yet.

31
00:02:13,130 --> 00:02:18,590
A few drops of his leftover blood condensed into a Five-Colored Stone.

32
00:02:18,590 --> 00:02:22,610
And now, Di Feitian is about to come out.

33
00:02:22,610 --> 00:02:28,510
The one who awakens him will be a girl who owns the Five-Colored Stone.

34
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:33,130
You are the one predestined by the Mystic Spirit Leaf.

35
00:02:33,130 --> 00:02:36,590
Only you can change the universe.

36
00:02:36,590 --> 00:02:39,320
Find the girl with the Five-Colored Stone.

37
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:44,850
Or else, the Five Regions will once again be doomed eternally because of her.

38
00:03:50,570 --> 00:03:52,910
- Who comes here?
- Fuyao.

39
00:03:52,910 --> 00:03:55,000
For the third level of the Mystic Soul Five-Way Technique,

40
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:57,470
the person who can obtain the emblem of the Mystic Soul can get through this level.

41
00:03:57,470 --> 00:04:00,470
Okay. Then let's give it a try.

42
00:06:21,190 --> 00:06:24,750
How dare you! Why don't you bow when you see your senior sister!

43
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:29,240
Senior Sister Pei is really merciless when she fights.

44
00:06:30,100 --> 00:06:32,450
As a lowly factotum of Mystic Black Section,

45
00:06:32,450 --> 00:06:34,500
