46
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:37,380
Don't think that just because First Senior Brother secretly taught you some Kung Fu,

47
00:06:37,380 --> 00:06:39,490
you can have the same level and same treatment as I.

48
00:06:39,490 --> 00:06:43,660
Someone of low status will forever be of low status.

49
00:06:43,660 --> 00:06:45,670
Some level and same treatment?

50
00:06:45,670 --> 00:06:46,920
That's good.

51
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:51,120
But unfortunately, I almost learned that Kung Fu.

52
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,860
You wish!

53
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:56,710
You violated the rules of Mystic Soul and privately entered Five-Way Sanctum to cultivate.

54
00:06:56,710 --> 00:07:00,470
Today, I will definitely bring you to see Clique Leader.

55
00:07:00,470 --> 00:07:03,880
I'd like to see who would speak up for you.

56
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,460
Just a minute, just a minute.

57
00:07:05,460 --> 00:07:08,580
Senior Sister, I did violate the clique rules.

58
00:07:08,580 --> 00:07:10,710
You want to bring me to Clique Leader for punishment.

59
00:07:10,710 --> 00:07:13,350
However, if you want to catch the thief, you must also have the loot.

60
00:07:13,350 --> 00:07:15,080
You have to catch me first.

61
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:18,660
Your death is imminent and yet you are still stubborn with your words.

62
00:07:23,470 --> 00:07:25,390
A'Lie, tie her up!

63
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:26,840
Yes.

64
00:07:41,570 --> 00:07:43,260
You are indeed an idiot.

65
00:07:43,260 --> 00:07:45,200
Below lies the bottomless cliff.

66
00:07:45,200 --> 00:07:47,780
If you have the ability, then jump.

67
00:07:47,780 --> 00:07:50,040
I am so scared.

68
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:52,880
But since my senior sister has commanded me to do so,

69
00:07:52,880 --> 00:07:55,410
I will have to follow.

70
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,040
Miss.

71
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,970
Idiot!

72
00:08:09,740 --> 00:08:11,710
This lowly servant!

73
00:08:11,710 --> 00:08:13,660
You will pay for it!

74
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:47,650
First Senior Brother!

75
00:08:47,650 --> 00:08:49,100
Fuyao!

76
00:08:49,100 --> 00:08:50,490
I saw someone from really far away.

77
00:08:50,490 --> 00:08:52,380
I knew it was you.

78
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:55,230
Why did you sneak out and come down the mountain again?

79
00:08:55,230 --> 00:08:57,870
I told you many times already, you can't sneak down on your own!

80
00:08:57,870 --> 00:08:59,110
If you get found out, you will be—

81
00:08:59,110 --> 00:09:01,090
I know! I just miss you!

82
00:09:01,090 --> 00:09:03,310
Full of nonsense!

83
00:09:04,590 --> 00:09:06,000
First Senior Brother.

84
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,280
Junior Sister.

85
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:11,240
Senior Brother, you can't cover for this lowly servant today anymore.

86
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,330
She is extremely daring.

87
00:09:12,330 --> 00:09:14,780
She actually dared to secretly enter the cultivation sanctum to cultivate.

88
00:09:14,780 --> 00:09:16,110
And she was escaping by running down the mountain.

89
00:09:16,110 --> 00:09:18,330
Who knows how many clique rules she has violated?

90
00:09:18,330 --> 00:09:20,420
About this, we must report to Clique Leader!

91
00:09:20,420 --> 00:09:22,090
She must be severely punished!

92
00:09:22,790 --> 00:09:25,250
Did that really happen?

93
00:09:25,250 --> 00:09:26,710
Yes.

94
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:33,050
You! You always act so recklessly!

95
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:38,280
Junior Sister Pei, Fuyao is still young.

96
00:09:38,280 --> 00:09:39,650
