98
00:09:42,020 --> 00:09:45,900
First Senior Brother! You always cover up for her like this!

99
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:48,850
This lowly servant of Mystic Black Section will disregard the rules even more so!

100
00:09:48,850 --> 00:09:50,910
Will our Mt. Mystic Soul still have rules then?

101
00:09:50,910 --> 00:09:54,450
Speaking of rules, Senior Sister Pei Yuan isn't any better.

102
00:09:54,450 --> 00:09:56,480
You! How dare you!

103
00:09:56,480 --> 00:10:00,120
Did I say anything wrong? Today is the day of the sacrificial ritual.

104
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:03,930
All of the students of Mystic Main Section should be waiting on the mountain.

105
00:10:03,930 --> 00:10:07,100
Senior Sister Pei Yuan is the First Senior Sister of Mystic Main Section after all.

106
00:10:07,100 --> 00:10:09,200
Why did you secretly go down the mountain, too?

107
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,590
You!

108
00:10:10,590 --> 00:10:12,390
Junior Sister Pei,

109
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:15,290
you are right in scolding her.

110
00:10:15,290 --> 00:10:17,710
I will report to Clique Leader later.

111
00:10:17,710 --> 00:10:19,930
I will make sure that she gets punished.

112
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:24,390
You! When you go back,

113
00:10:24,390 --> 00:10:27,000
