116
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:35,090
Yes.

117
00:10:36,690 --> 00:10:40,000
First Senior Brother! Why did you let her go just like that?

118
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,620
Junior Sister!

119
00:10:55,220 --> 00:10:57,080
It's almost time.

120
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:59,660
Why don't you follow me to join the sacrificial ritual?

121
00:10:59,660 --> 00:11:02,220
Sacrificial ritual?

122
00:11:21,610 --> 00:11:23,620
- Greetings, Father.
- Greetings, Teacher.

123
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:48,940
We're going to have the Hunting and Fighting Game soon in our Mystic Soul.

124
00:11:48,940 --> 00:11:51,700
Under the blessing, we have peace and prosperity.

125
00:11:51,700 --> 00:11:55,750
To the ancestors and masters, Student Yan Lie would like to ask you

126
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:59,100
