146
00:13:09,380 --> 00:13:10,990
Come here. Come here.

147
00:13:12,790 --> 00:13:14,830
I’m telling you,

148
00:13:16,130 --> 00:13:20,670
we have food and shelter here with

149
00:13:20,670 --> 00:13:24,670
