150
00:13:24,670 --> 00:13:28,140
How blessed we are.

151
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:33,080
You have to work hard here, never think of useless things.

152
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:37,610
Don’t be like the children leader, Fuyao.

153
00:13:37,610 --> 00:13:41,910
I’m telling you, this Older Sis Fuyao—

154
00:13:43,090 --> 00:13:45,750
[Fuyao]

155
00:13:48,850 --> 00:13:53,990
Where is Fuyao? Where is Fuyao?

156
00:13:53,990 --> 00:13:56,010
Where did Fuyao go?

157
00:13:56,010 --> 00:13:59,550
Help us at Mystic Soul to peacefully control Deep Water Nation

158
00:13:59,550 --> 00:14:01,750
and win over the five regions again.

159
00:14:01,750 --> 00:14:05,500
Help us at Mystic Soul to peacefully control Deep Water Nation

160
00:14:05,500 --> 00:14:08,270
- and win over the five regions again.
- You scared me, Older Sis Fuyao.

161
00:14:08,270 --> 00:14:10,010
Why did you just get here?

162
00:14:10,010 --> 00:14:13,000
You look quite handsome in this. Where is mine? Where is mine?

163
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,910
- Here. Here.
- Let me see.

164
00:14:14,910 --> 00:14:18,200
You tell me. It's bad enough we wear cyan garments to pretend as someone in Mystic Main Section.

165
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:21,090
What if someone finds out that we are watching Clique Leader's sacrificial ritual secretly?

166
00:14:21,090 --> 00:14:22,330
I can’t imagine how we will die.

167
00:14:22,330 --> 00:14:24,500
There're so many people in Mystic Main Section.

168
00:14:24,500 --> 00:14:27,420
Who will notice whom?

169
00:14:27,420 --> 00:14:30,160
If we’re being so secretive like you,

170
00:14:30,160 --> 00:14:32,140
we will look more suspicious. Be like me.

171
00:14:32,140 --> 00:14:34,160
Right, no one will recognize me.

172
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:37,040
But you're a trouble maker. How will no one know you?

173
00:14:37,040 --> 00:14:39,680
This Hunting and Fighting Game is only held once per eight years.

174
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:41,880
Of course, we have to watch the sacrificial ritual.

175
00:14:41,880 --> 00:14:43,740
We can learn something.

176
00:14:43,740 --> 00:14:45,060
If I'd known, I wouldn't take you here.

177
00:14:45,060 --> 00:14:47,770
Don’t be like this. I’m going. I’m going.

178
00:16:03,590 --> 00:16:09,670
Starting today, we are taking applications for the once-per-eight-year Hunting and Fighting Game.

179
00:16:09,670 --> 00:16:11,640
As long as you’re an adult student under our clique,

180
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:16,170
no matter if you’re wearing white, cyan or red garments, you can apply for it.

181
00:16:16,170 --> 00:16:18,940
No judging based on your background but your skills.

182
00:16:18,940 --> 00:16:22,780
The Hunting and Fighting Game was established by our clique founder for him to form the clique.

183
00:16:22,780 --> 00:16:26,300
With many levels, it's established in order to select the bravest student

184
00:16:26,300 --> 00:16:29,680
and help the citizens to get rid of the mountain beasts.

185
00:16:29,680 --> 00:16:32,950
The winner will be the hero. What’s a hero?

186
00:16:32,950 --> 00:16:37,010
A person with the plant essence as his content and the animal's power as his strength.

187
00:16:37,010 --> 00:16:39,650
Today’s winner will still be a hero.

188
00:16:39,650 --> 00:16:42,170
He will carry the honor of Mystic Soul Clique

189
00:16:42,170 --> 00:16:44,700
and be the pillar of Deep Water Nation.

190
00:16:44,700 --> 00:16:48,170
This is a game with both tests and honor.

191
00:16:48,170 --> 00:16:49,820
Whoever wants to participate

192
00:16:49,820 --> 00:16:54,140
has to put the application with your own blood into this Celestial Fangding.

193
00:16:54,140 --> 00:16:57,560
Once you participate in it, your life depends on the game.

194
00:16:57,560 --> 00:16:59,140
Never regret.

195
00:16:59,140 --> 00:17:01,290
Not judging by our background.

196
00:17:01,820 --> 00:17:05,200
They’re still looking down on us from Mystic Black Section, who’s wearing black garments.

197
00:17:06,940 --> 00:17:08,500
Am I wrong?

198
00:17:09,360 --> 00:17:10,910
Do you want to die?

199
00:17:10,910 --> 00:17:14,060
Quickly leave. Leave. Leave. Hurry. Hurry.

200
00:17:16,030 --> 00:17:19,080
Come down. Come down.

201
00:17:19,080 --> 00:17:21,960
Are you bullying me who doesn’t know how to climb up the tree?

202
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:27,890
I’m telling you! I’m going to beat you to death if you come down.

203
00:17:27,890 --> 00:17:29,900
Is the sacrificial ritual somewhere you're allowed to go?

204
00:17:29,900 --> 00:17:33,880
It's not enough to cause the trouble to yourself. You even dragged him in.

205
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:36,400
Are you coming down or not? Coming down or not?

206
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:39,920
I want to go down but I’m afraid of heights, I can’t go down.

207
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:42,570
- This kid—
- Uncle Zhou, don’t be angry. Don't be angry.

208
00:17:42,570 --> 00:17:44,430
Older Sis Fuyao, quickly beg Uncle Zhou.

209
00:17:44,430 --> 00:17:47,020
If you’re helping her, don’t stop me then. If not, I going to beat you, too.

210
00:17:47,020 --> 00:17:50,030
- I'm going to beat you—
- Stop it. Stop it. Don’t beat him.

211
00:17:50,030 --> 00:17:52,450
- I forced him to go.
- No! It wasn't Older Sis Fuyao who forced me to go.

212
00:17:52,450 --> 00:17:54,750
- I went voluntarily. This really has—
- I don’t cared if you went voluntarily or not,

213
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:56,180
go back and finish your dyeing jobs.

214
00:17:56,180 --> 00:17:57,670
- Okay. Okay.
- Quickly leave.

215
00:17:57,670 --> 00:18:00,230
- Leave.
- Go. Hurry up.

216
00:18:03,180 --> 00:18:06,630
Come on, Uncle Zhou. You see, he left.

217
00:18:06,630 --> 00:18:08,660
Stop scolding me.

218
00:18:08,660 --> 00:18:10,840
And I went there just to watch.

219
00:18:10,840 --> 00:18:13,140
No one saw me.

220
00:18:14,390 --> 00:18:16,190
Come down.

221
00:18:16,990 --> 00:18:19,160
Come down and I won’t beat you.

222
00:18:22,730 --> 00:18:24,600
Come down and I will give you a interesting job.

223
00:18:24,600 --> 00:18:26,430
I see.

224
00:18:26,430 --> 00:18:28,660
Today’s the 15th.

225
00:18:30,170 --> 00:18:32,720
Go down the mountain to get some wine.

226
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:34,080
You’re letting me go down the mountain?

227
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:37,320
If you’re not going, I will ask someone else.

228
00:18:38,290 --> 00:18:40,890
You. Finally you came down.

229
00:18:40,890 --> 00:18:44,220
Where did you go? You even climbed the tree, didn't you?

230
00:18:44,220 --> 00:18:47,300
It’s painful.

231
00:18:48,650 --> 00:18:51,520
Stop hitting me. My butt hurts.

232
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:54,880
Get up. Here.

233
00:18:57,420 --> 00:18:59,110
Let me see.

234
00:19:02,590 --> 00:19:04,570
Look at you, kid. I want to beat you till you're clear.

235
00:19:04,570 --> 00:19:07,040
I really want to beat you a few more times.

236
00:19:09,670 --> 00:19:15,860
Fuyao, be honest, why isn’t our Mystic Black Section good?

237
00:19:16,550 --> 00:19:20,650
Right. Our rank is low. We’re poor.

238
00:19:20,650 --> 00:19:23,930
But everyone treats you so well.

239
00:19:23,930 --> 00:19:27,230
Xiaoqi, that group of children follows you around every day. And what are you teaching them?

240
00:19:27,230 --> 00:19:29,300
Teaching them to be like you and climb trees?

241
00:19:29,300 --> 00:19:31,290
You are always thinking of ways to take off your black garment, right?

242
00:19:31,290 --> 00:19:33,120
What's wrong with me?

243
00:19:33,120 --> 00:19:35,220
I have a pretty good relationship with everyone at Mystic Black Section.

244
00:19:35,220 --> 00:19:37,400
My relation with Xiaobai is also quite good.

245
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:40,790
- Then be a little more obedient.
- When was I disobedient?

246
00:19:40,790 --> 00:19:42,610
I just think it's unfair.

247
00:19:42,610 --> 00:19:44,530
Why do people have to be ranked in different levels and status?

248
00:19:44,530 --> 00:19:46,720
Look at the people at Mystic Main Section.

249
00:19:46,720 --> 00:19:49,490
They can learn martial arts as soon as they get in, and go wherever they want to go.

250
00:19:49,490 --> 00:19:52,150
And they even bully us! And yet we have to serve them.

251
00:19:52,150 --> 00:19:55,400
Why is this? So our lives are just worthless, right?

252
00:19:55,400 --> 00:19:57,680
Stop talking anymore. This is all fate.

253
00:19:57,680 --> 00:20:01,210
It's fate so you will just have to accept it.

254
00:20:01,210 --> 00:20:03,070
I am going!

255
00:20:03,070 --> 00:20:07,060
Hey! When you are out, you can't cause troubles! Did you hear me? Okay?

256
00:20:07,060 --> 00:20:09,930
- Did you hear me?
- I heard you!

257
00:20:11,300 --> 00:20:13,190
Did you get anything out of this three-month trip?

258
00:20:13,190 --> 00:20:16,260
In my trip to Capital Kun, I was able to meet with the crown prince.

259
00:20:16,260 --> 00:20:19,050
The crown prince is kind and friendly with a manner of sage.

260
00:20:19,050 --> 00:20:21,440
I was fortunate to be appreciated by the crown prince.

261
00:20:21,440 --> 00:20:24,060
His Highness said that there are all kinds of parties among the officials.

262
00:20:24,060 --> 00:20:25,700
He wants to build his own troops.

263
00:20:25,700 --> 00:20:28,560
And I am the person that he needs.

264
00:20:28,560 --> 00:20:32,100
On your way back, you didn't hear any news?

265
00:20:32,100 --> 00:20:33,830
What news?

266
00:20:37,570 --> 00:20:39,670
There is mutiny in Capital Kun.

267
00:20:39,670 --> 00:20:41,160
What?

268
00:20:42,280 --> 00:20:44,880
[Capital Kun, Deep Water Nation]

269
00:20:56,590 --> 00:20:58,190
King Father.

270
00:21:03,560 --> 00:21:08,360
Have you taken care of the things I ordered you to do?

271
00:21:08,360 --> 00:21:13,490
King Father, I have appointed Zhang Henian to arrange troops in the palace.

272
00:21:13,490 --> 00:21:17,440
The garrisons and the eight units of guards are already outside of the city walls.

273
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:22,930
It's impossible for Qi Zhen to escape this time even if he has wings.

274
00:21:22,930 --> 00:21:26,030
Good. Good.

275
00:21:26,030 --> 00:21:31,150
Qi Zhen has coveted my throne for quite a while.

276
00:21:31,150 --> 00:21:34,930
In three days, it will be your enthronement day.

277
00:21:35,480 --> 00:21:41,530
If we don't get rid of Qi Zhen, my royal bloodline of Xuanyuan will be in danger.

278
00:21:42,620 --> 00:21:49,070
Remember. Root and branch.

279
00:21:52,990 --> 00:21:57,120
Root and branch.

280
00:22:30,330 --> 00:22:35,540
Tonight, Deep Water will be mine!

281
00:22:50,380 --> 00:22:51,900
[Qi Zhen had his eyes on the nation a long time ago...]

282
00:22:51,900 --> 00:22:55,600
Could Qi Zhen really dare to harm His Majesty?

283
00:22:56,600 --> 00:22:58,600
He is the state's prime minister.

284
00:22:58,600 --> 00:23:01,500
He is already just below one and above so many.

285
00:23:01,500 --> 00:23:05,900
Usurping the throne is a major event that will bring disaster to the five regions.

286
00:23:07,750 --> 00:23:10,030
Qi Zhen is holding too much power.

287
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:14,200
His battle with the royal family of Xuanyuan will happen sooner or later.

288
00:23:14,200 --> 00:23:18,400
I just don't know who will be victorious in this battle.

289
00:23:19,600 --> 00:23:22,400
Once the Xuanyuan clan is annihilated and a new ruler emerges,

290
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:26,000
the order in Deep Water will be rebuilt.

291
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:30,400
Is our Mystic Soul Clique just going to sit by and watch?

292
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:32,800
What then must we do?

293
00:23:32,800 --> 00:23:35,800
Our Mystic Soul is part of jianghu and doesn't intervene with power struggles.

294
00:23:35,800 --> 00:23:39,700
Not siding with anyone and just sitting by to observe the consequences is the exact righteous path.

295
00:23:39,700 --> 00:23:43,500
It's just that Chen'er has received His Majesty's graces.

296
00:23:43,500 --> 00:23:45,100
I feel a bit—

297
00:23:45,100 --> 00:23:47,200
In the fight for power, there are no personal feelings.

298
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:49,600
As long as you are able to get the fist in the Hunting and Fighting Game,

299
00:23:49,600 --> 00:23:52,400
with our position in the martial arts society,

300
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:55,200
with you being the top fighter in the Hunting and Fighting Game,

301
00:23:55,200 --> 00:23:57,600
will you still be afraid that no one will admire your skills?

302
00:23:57,600 --> 00:23:59,600
What Father taught is correct.

303
00:23:59,600 --> 00:24:03,100
Prepare well. In this Hunting and Fighting Game this time,

304
00:24:03,100 --> 00:24:05,200
you have to win.

305
00:24:05,200 --> 00:24:06,800
Yes.

306
00:24:42,700 --> 00:24:44,100
Heir Apparent.

307
00:24:45,320 --> 00:24:47,020
Prime Minister?

308
00:24:48,300 --> 00:24:51,200
I observed the celestial bodies and noticed that it will be a starless night today.

309
00:24:51,200 --> 00:24:55,300
There will be a bloody disaster happening in the palace.

310
00:24:56,300 --> 00:24:57,500
Convey my orders,

311
00:24:57,500 --> 00:25:01,400
kill all the bloodlines of the Xuanyuan clan.

312
00:25:14,600 --> 00:25:18,000
Hurry and lay down. Come.

313
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:21,960
Don't worry.

314
00:25:21,960 --> 00:25:24,000
No one will kill you.

315
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:27,100
Who would dare to bear the infamous reputation of killing the king?

316
00:25:27,100 --> 00:25:29,400
Just hold on for a little while more.

317
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:34,000
You then can watch me take over the royal throne of Deep Water.

318
00:26:16,890 --> 00:26:19,450
How are you? Hello?

319
00:26:20,700 --> 00:26:23,600
Save me. I'm the son of Prince Quandu, Xuanyuan Min.

320
00:26:23,600 --> 00:26:26,600
Save me! Save me!

321
00:26:26,600 --> 00:26:28,400
Save me.

322
00:26:53,700 --> 00:26:55,000
Senior Sister Pei.

323
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:56,300
This net will tighten the more you struggle.

324
00:26:56,300 --> 00:27:00,600
For ordinary people, it's impossible to cut through them and escape in less than three hours.

325
00:27:00,600 --> 00:27:04,400
As long as we're able to teach that Fuyao a lesson this time, I won't forget to reward you.

326
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:05,900
Thanks, Senior Sister.

327
00:27:46,420 --> 00:27:48,100
Hello, Big Bro.

328
00:27:48,100 --> 00:27:49,400
Save me, Big Bro!

329
00:27:49,400 --> 00:27:52,500
Wait a minute! Hello!

330
00:28:45,400 --> 00:28:47,300
I've caught you.

331
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:52,800
Junior Sister Pei?

332
00:28:52,800 --> 00:28:56,400
Sorry, sorry. I thought it was Fuyao.

333
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:59,400
What? Do I look like Fuyao?

334
00:28:59,400 --> 00:29:01,400
No. You guys don't look alike.

335
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:04,300
I just thought...

336
00:29:05,360 --> 00:29:08,320
Why did Junior Sister Pei come here?

337
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:13,400
Senior Brother and Fuyao can come. Can I not come?

338
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:15,600
That is not what I meant.

339
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:18,800
If that's the case, then I'll—

340
00:29:18,800 --> 00:29:22,500
When Senior Brother went out to travel, summer was just starting.

341
00:29:22,500 --> 00:29:25,890
Look. In a blink of an eye, it's already the season to wear extra clothes.

342
00:29:25,890 --> 00:29:27,500
It's exactly three months and nine days.

343
00:29:27,500 --> 00:29:29,350
Oh, wrong!

344
00:29:29,350 --> 00:29:32,800
Counting today, it's exactly one hundred days.

345
00:29:32,800 --> 00:29:35,200
Since my eldest sister got married off,

346
00:29:35,200 --> 00:29:38,200
Father kept wanting me to establish a marriage alliance with the House of the Prime Minister

347
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:40,800
and rushing me to return to the capital.

348
00:29:42,700 --> 00:29:44,170
When a woman has grown up, she should be married off.

349
00:29:44,170 --> 00:29:46,200
Junior Sister has indeed reached the age to get married.

350
00:29:46,200 --> 00:29:48,500
Does First Senior Brother still not understand?

351
00:29:49,430 --> 00:29:52,200
I just want to stay in Mt. Mystic Soul.

352
00:29:52,200 --> 00:29:54,400
I want to be with First Senior Brother—

353
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:59,200
Junior Sister Pei's martial arts is one of the best here in Mystic Soul Clique for the past years.

354
00:29:59,200 --> 00:30:02,200
I'm sure you'll have an outstanding performance during the Hunting and Fighting Game.

355
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:04,420
By then, you will surely become famous throughout Deep Water.

356
00:30:04,420 --> 00:30:05,900
Not only the House of the Prime Minister,

357
00:30:05,900 --> 00:30:10,200
even the royal family will compete to marry you.

358
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:15,000
I indeed don't want to return to Capital Kun because I want to join the Hunting and Fighting Game,

359
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:16,910
but it's not for me.

360
00:30:16,910 --> 00:30:18,900
It's for First Senior Brother.

361
00:30:19,700 --> 00:30:24,240
I want to let First Senior Brother become famous throughout Deep Water.

362
00:30:26,600 --> 00:30:28,270
Who put this? Let me go!

363
00:30:28,270 --> 00:30:29,700
Put me down!

364
00:30:29,700 --> 00:30:32,100
Which bastard is it?

365
00:30:32,100 --> 00:30:34,400
How come it's this move again?

366
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:36,900
Who's there?

367
00:30:41,300 --> 00:30:44,200
Senior Brother, my feelings—

368
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:46,910
Help!

369
00:30:46,910 --> 00:30:49,600
Save me!

370
00:30:49,600 --> 00:30:52,500
- Help!
- It's Fuyao!

371
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:23,880
- Have you confirmed his identity?
- He indeed is Xuanyuan Min, a royal relative from Quandu.

372
00:31:23,880 --> 00:31:26,500
He indeed is the son of Prince Quandu, Xuanyuan Min.

373
00:31:29,000 --> 00:31:30,800
Kill him.

374
00:31:35,100 --> 00:31:37,800
Official Yun Heng, Prime Minister has ordered to keep him alive.

375
00:31:37,800 --> 00:31:39,200
Wait.

376
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:42,900
He seems to be dead.

377
00:31:44,900 --> 00:31:46,700
Help!

378
00:31:47,260 --> 00:31:48,700
Help!

379
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:51,500
Fuyao!

380
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:55,100
First Senior Brother!

381
00:31:55,820 --> 00:31:57,520
First Senior Brother!

382
00:32:03,800 --> 00:32:06,500
How are you? Are you all right?

383
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:07,800
I'm all right.

384
00:32:07,800 --> 00:32:10,000
Didn't you go down to stock up on rice wines?

385
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:11,680
How did you end up in this state?

386
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:13,400
Are you injured?

387
00:32:13,400 --> 00:32:14,930
Rice wines?

388
00:32:14,930 --> 00:32:17,000
I'm doomed. Doomed.

389
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:20,810
- I'm doomed.
- What's wrong, Fuyao?

390
00:32:20,810 --> 00:32:22,200
I'm doomed.

391
00:32:25,500 --> 00:32:28,700
Oh, no! Uncle Zhou will surely beat me to death.

392
00:32:28,700 --> 00:32:31,800
Look at you. Always being unfocused on your work.

393
00:32:31,800 --> 00:32:34,900
Forget it. I'll just explain things to Uncle Zhou next time.

394
00:32:36,500 --> 00:32:39,400
What are you looking for? What's wrong?

395
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:41,100
What are you looking for?

396
00:32:43,600 --> 00:32:48,500
First Senior Brother, when you were passing by just then, did you see a man that was injured?

397
00:32:48,500 --> 00:32:49,780
What time is it right now?

398
00:32:49,780 --> 00:32:53,000
Do you still have time to worry about other people's issues?

399
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,800
Who cares.

400
00:32:54,800 --> 00:32:56,900
I hope he's all right.

401
00:32:59,300 --> 00:33:02,000
Look at you. You're already injured yourself

402
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:04,800
and you still have time to worry about others people's issues.

403
00:33:07,000 --> 00:33:09,990
Fuyao, you're a girl.

404
00:33:09,990 --> 00:33:12,000
A girl should be like a girl.

405
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:14,500
You need to know how to cry, know that you suffered,

406
00:33:14,500 --> 00:33:16,610
and make someone's heart ache because of you.

407
00:33:17,300 --> 00:33:21,000
First Senior Brother, are you concerned about me?

408
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:23,900
Silly girl.

409
00:33:23,900 --> 00:33:27,000
Come. Sit over there and let me see your wound.

410
00:33:29,390 --> 00:33:32,400
Look at this, it's bleeding.

411
00:33:41,600 --> 00:33:46,290
I know that because I treat you well and special,

412
00:33:46,290 --> 00:33:48,640
there will always be some people mistreating you.

413
00:33:50,140 --> 00:33:54,400
This incident today must have been done by someone who purposely bullied you.

414
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:58,270
I know all of your grievances.

415
00:33:58,270 --> 00:34:00,650
I don't feel wronged.

416
00:34:00,650 --> 00:34:03,350
Whoever bullies me, I'll bully them as a return.

417
00:34:03,350 --> 00:34:06,260
You really like to act strong.

418
00:34:06,260 --> 00:34:09,250
You know that being extremely strong also makes you break easily.

419
00:34:10,570 --> 00:34:12,700
But don't worry, Fuyao.

420
00:34:12,700 --> 00:34:15,300
When I become the Leader of Mystic Soul Clique,

421
00:34:15,300 --> 00:34:18,470
I'll let you get rid of the slave identity.

422
00:34:18,470 --> 00:34:22,350
Then, I'll let you be proud and make everyone know that

423
00:34:22,350 --> 00:34:25,000
you are Yan Jingchen's woman.

424
00:34:35,410 --> 00:34:38,250
With First Older Brother's words,

425
00:34:38,250 --> 00:34:41,500
no matter what I've been through, it's nothing anymore.

426
00:34:43,120 --> 00:34:44,970
But I've been wondering

427
00:34:44,970 --> 00:34:47,600
how great it would be if First Senior Brother can treat

428
00:34:47,600 --> 00:34:49,610
the students in Mystic Black Section the way you treat me

429
00:34:49,610 --> 00:34:54,520
and let them take off their black garments soon.

430
00:34:55,190 --> 00:34:58,090
Mt. Mystic Soul has its own rules.

431
00:35:00,430 --> 00:35:03,380
Enough. Enough. Why are we talking about this?

432
00:35:03,380 --> 00:35:05,870
I'll send you back.

433
00:35:05,870 --> 00:35:07,300
Let's go.

434
00:35:12,800 --> 00:35:14,800
Someone has trespassed the mountain.

435
00:35:21,010 --> 00:35:24,620
Someone trespassed? Who dared?

436
00:35:24,620 --> 00:35:27,630
The trespasser claims that he is a subordinate of Prime Minister Qi Zhen.

437
00:35:33,540 --> 00:35:37,370
Our Mystic Soul Clique occupies Deep Water and leads the five regions.

438
00:35:37,370 --> 00:35:41,160
Who said someone like you could trespass at your own will?

439
00:35:41,160 --> 00:35:43,490
Clique Leader is here.

440
00:35:52,520 --> 00:35:55,340
I am Yan Lie, Clique Leader of Mystic Soul Clique.

441
00:35:55,340 --> 00:35:58,030
May I ask why you trespassed into our clique's territory?

442
00:35:58,030 --> 00:36:01,240
You do have a few good doctors in Mt. Mystic Soul, don't you?

443
00:36:01,240 --> 00:36:03,110
We have an injured man.

444
00:36:03,110 --> 00:36:06,520
He is someone that Official Qi, Qi Zhen of Deep Water has requested to save.

445
00:36:06,520 --> 00:36:09,010
I assume that you may have stayed so long in Capital Kun

446
00:36:09,010 --> 00:36:12,350
that you've forgotten what manner one should have when asking for a favor.

447
00:36:12,350 --> 00:36:14,950
Prime Minister is here.

448
00:36:21,430 --> 00:36:23,840
[Mystic Soul Heights]

449
00:36:57,610 --> 00:37:00,560
Is the doctor inside knowledgeable or not?

450
00:37:00,560 --> 00:37:03,410
Prime Minister, don't panic.

451
00:37:03,410 --> 00:37:08,720
The doctor inside is the jianghu-renowned medical sage, Zhong Yue.

452
00:37:09,690 --> 00:37:13,280
Doctor Zhong only comes up the mountains to pick medicine when fall comes.

453
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:16,070
Or else, his tracks are hard to find.

454
00:37:18,030 --> 00:37:22,190
A treatment from him will surely heal the illness when the medicine takes effect.

455
00:37:23,250 --> 00:37:25,790
A medical sage?

456
00:37:25,790 --> 00:37:30,020
Let's hope he doesn't only have the name.

457
00:37:37,430 --> 00:37:39,440
Has the patient recovered?

458
00:37:39,440 --> 00:37:40,780
There is nothing wrong with him.

459
00:37:40,780 --> 00:37:43,780
He will sure awaken within an hour.

460
00:37:44,660 --> 00:37:48,440
Then, please, I trouble Sir to write the patient a prescription.

461
00:37:48,440 --> 00:37:50,950
I've said, there is nothing wrong with him.

462
00:37:50,950 --> 00:37:52,530
There is no need for medication.

463
00:37:52,530 --> 00:37:54,080
I'll take my leave.

464
00:37:56,130 --> 00:37:57,700
How disrespectful.

465
00:38:00,370 --> 00:38:02,380
Forget it. Forget it.

466
00:38:04,800 --> 00:38:07,240
Since he is a common medical sage,

467
00:38:07,240 --> 00:38:11,050
he surely will have some arrogance of disregarding the king's power.

468
00:38:32,120 --> 00:38:34,790
He indeed is Xuanyuan Min, a royal relative from Quandu.

469
00:38:43,350 --> 00:38:44,820
Father.

470
00:38:46,630 --> 00:38:49,020
What happened, Father?

471
00:38:49,020 --> 00:38:52,990
Pass down the orders that they need to serve cautiously in the next few days.

472
00:38:52,990 --> 00:38:55,230
Who is inside exactly?

473
00:38:57,550 --> 00:38:59,990
The Prime Minister of Deep Water Nation, Qi Zhen.

474
00:39:01,040 --> 00:39:03,490
Qi Zhen comes to our Mt. Mystic Soul at this time.

475
00:39:03,490 --> 00:39:06,580
I am afraid it's because there is mutiny in the palace.

476
00:39:06,580 --> 00:39:11,400
But to you, this will be a good opportunity.

477
00:39:41,550 --> 00:39:43,260
Who are you?

478
00:39:44,500 --> 00:39:47,130
Wh-Where is this?

479
00:39:59,260 --> 00:40:02,950
Are you really the son of Prince Quandu,

480
00:40:02,950 --> 00:40:05,430
Xuanyuan Min?

481
00:40:09,810 --> 00:40:11,560
If yes, so what?

482
00:40:15,430 --> 00:40:17,610
If not, what then?

483
00:40:44,780 --> 00:40:48,120
The royal Xuanyuan clan's Water Manipulation Technique

484
00:40:48,950 --> 00:40:52,360
is really true to its name.

485
00:40:52,360 --> 00:40:54,490
Who are you exactly?

486
00:40:55,870 --> 00:40:58,360
How do you also know this secret?

487
00:41:03,130 --> 00:41:05,600
I am Qi Zhen. Greetings, Your Highness Heir Apparent.

488
00:41:05,600 --> 00:41:09,950
Hope Your Highness Heir Apparent can forgive me from disturbing you.

489
00:41:14,220 --> 00:41:17,790
Heir-Heir Apparent?

490
00:41:21,960 --> 00:41:24,070
Who is Heir Apparent that you're talking about?

491
00:41:25,040 --> 00:41:29,590
It looks like the king's decree from Capital Kun hasn't reached you yet.

492
00:41:29,590 --> 00:41:34,790
Your Highness, the King has conferred you Heir Apparent of Deep Water.

493
00:41:34,790 --> 00:41:38,450
The welcoming troupe will arrive in one to two days.

494
00:41:50,070 --> 00:41:51,660
Is this for real?

495
00:41:51,660 --> 00:41:56,010
What do you think, Heir Apparent?

496
00:42:01,490 --> 00:42:03,530
Then this means...

497
00:42:03,530 --> 00:42:06,070
I'll...

498
00:42:10,950 --> 00:42:13,490
I will be the king of Deep Water in the future.

499
00:42:15,860 --> 00:42:18,190
That's right.

500
00:42:26,610 --> 00:42:28,410
Okay.

501
00:42:32,590 --> 00:42:34,820
